<p>The good life! The mother-of-four rented out a 5-star villa at the Sheraton Grand Resort Hotel on the Gold Coast for herself and two of her daughters </p>

<p>Expensive taste! The model mum was showered with expensive gifts on her special day, including Moet champagne and a gold necklace from Tiffany &amp; Co.</p>

<p>In a year and-a-half, Gina claims to have earned around $500,000 on the platform.</p>

